k\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-WilnerGenie_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Wilner, Norman (10 March 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nowtoronto.com/daily/movies/story.cfm?content=179583\">\"Divvying up the Genies\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Now_(newspaper)\" title=\"Now (newspaper)\">Now</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 March</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Now&amp;rft.atitle=Divvying+up+the+Genies&amp;rft.date=2011-03-10&amp;rft.aulast=Wilner&amp;rft.aufirst=Norman&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nowtoronto.com%2Fdaily%2Fmovies%2Fstory.cfm%3Fcontent%3D179583&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALipsett+Diaries\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Borowiecki-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Borowiecki_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Borowiecki, Anna (27 October 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.stalbertgazette.com/article/20101027/SAG0302/310279984/film-board-wants-to-animate-the-public\">\"Film board wants to animate the public\"</a>. <i>St. Albert Gazette</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">27 October</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=St.+Albert+Gazette&amp;rft.atitle=Film+board+wants+to+animate+the+public&amp;rft.date=2010-10-27&amp;rft.aulast=Borowiecki&amp;rft.aufirst=Anna&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stalbertgazette.com%2Farticle%2F20101027%2FSAG0302%2F310279984%2Ffilm-board-wants-to-animate-the-public&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALipsett+Diaries\" class=\"Z3988\"><spa